title: Deposit Interest Rate in Argentina
description: Deposit Interest Rate in Argentina was at 70.83 percent on Thursday November 10. Deposit Interest Rate in Argentina averaged 16.81 percent from 1994 until 2022, reaching an all time high of 85.38 percent in May of 2002 and a record low of 0 percent in January of 2002. The Deposit Interest Rate is the average rate paid by commercial banks to individuals or corporations on deposits. This page includes a chart with historical data for Deposit Interest Rate in Argentina.
author: Central Bank of Argentina
